column2: SELECT    m.RA_deg_# as input_ra, m.DEC_deg_# AS input_dec,    n.objid as sdssm_objid, n.distance as sdssm_distance,    s.z as sdss_s_z, s.class as sdss_s_class, s.subClass as sdss_s_subClass,    gz.p_mg as galzoo_mg,    dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as sdss_p_type into mydb.MyTable from MyDB.ESO_prop_radec AS m    OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.RA_deg_#, m.DEC_deg_#, #) AS n    LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objid = p.objid     LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID    LEFT JOIN ZooNoSpec AS gz on gz.specobjid = s.specobjid
